        <item>
            <title>Insta360 Ace Pro 2 疑中国下架，香港用家：对起雾极失望 + 应一早回收</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/19/insta360-ace-pro-2/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=insta360-ace-pro-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/19/insta360-ace-pro-2/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 07:00:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Insta360]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Insta360 Ace Pro 2]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275886</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">上月开卖的运动摄影机 Insta360 Ace Pro 2，被大量用家发现起雾问题，更有人扬言会转会至其他品牌，有网民指已知会客服但未获回复。中国各地暂时官方网店已全线「缺货」，疑似被下架；惟香港官方网店仍然有得卖。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275890 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241118at-8-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241118at-8-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241118at-8-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有用家上传影片，指 Insta360 Ace Pro 2 出现起雾问题（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q_B7EieMU6o">中年流浪猫 / ㄓˋㄩˋ</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">可以拍摄 8K 30fps 解像度影片及具备双 AI 晶片的 Insta360 Ace Pro 2，被网民发现有起雾问题。有网民在 Insta360 用家的 Facebook 群组内发文表示：「警世！救得一个得一个！Insta Ace pro 2 完全为失败之作！想买未买，唔好晒钱！！！」，并指推出至今，Insta360 都未有解决 Ace Pro 2 发热起雾问题，亦未有回收方案，客服一直回避问题，因此极度失望。有网民留言表示，趁有优惠价买 Ace Pro 1 比买 Ace Pro 2 更好，更指对 Ace Pro 2 没有信心，应一早回收。有网民指会转会至 DJI，更有人笑称 Ace Pro 2 像时光倒流 10 年前的 gopro，都有发热起雾问题。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275891 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-694x227.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="227" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-694x227.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民指：「Insta Ace pro 2 完全为失败之作！想买未买，唔好晒钱！！！」（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/insta360hk/permalink/2626872570833114/?rdid=tWogXf9Bsgq1Amg1&amp;share_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fp%2F17qqiuzRYm%2F">Insta360 Hong Kong User Group</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275892 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-1-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-1-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民留言表示，趁有优惠价买 Ace Pro 1 比买 Ace Pro 2 更好（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/insta360hk/permalink/2626872570833114/?rdid=tWogXf9Bsgq1Amg1&amp;share_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fp%2F17qqiuzRYm%2F">Insta360 Hong Kong User Group</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275894 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-3-694x262.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="262" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-3-694x262.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-3.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民留言表示 Ace Pro 2 应一早回收（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/insta360hk/permalink/2626872570833114/?rdid=tWogXf9Bsgq1Amg1&amp;share_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fp%2F17qqiuzRYm%2F">Insta360 Hong Kong User Group</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275893 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-2-694x380.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="380" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-2-694x380.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-2.jpg 1128w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民指会转会至 DJI（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/insta360hk/permalink/2626872570833114/?rdid=tWogXf9Bs