            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>平治推出全新旗舰电动房车 EQS 450+，将 EQS 系列电动房车全面升级，具高达 54 公里的额外续航距离，标准配备 AMG 风格、Electric Art 系列的全新鬼面罩和镀铬饰边，引擎盖上设有直立的平治星徽标志， 同时后座的舒适度亦有所提升。 EQS 450+ 现已于平治港岛品牌中心展出。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114910-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114910-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114910-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114910-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115006-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115006-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115006-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115006-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115140-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115140-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115140-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115140-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>全新 EQS 450+ 电池容量由 108.4 kWh 增加至 118 kWh，续航距离高达 839 公里，甚至超越 800 公里的里程标准， 更标配车门电动关闭功能。<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114422-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114422-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114422-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114422-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114601-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114601-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114601-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114601-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_120300-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275791" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_120300-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_120300-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_120300-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_120146-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275792" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_120146-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_120146-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_120146-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114645-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275793" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114645-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114645-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114645-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115341-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275800" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115341-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115341-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_115341-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>EQS 450+ B 柱出风口配备镀铬装饰，后座更增设额外坐垫并饰以 Nappa 真皮饰边，Comfort 座椅及 Executive 座椅皆标配前座头枕靠垫。EQS 450+ 亦标配 MBUX Hyperscreen 超萤幕，一片玻璃板面下实际蕴藏 3 个显示器，创造出一面超过 141 厘米宽的大型超萤幕。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114741-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114741-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114741-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114741-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114818-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275799" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114818-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114818-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114818-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114142-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275808" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114142-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114142-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114142-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114203-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114203-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114203-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114203-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114310-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275798" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114310-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114310-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241118_114310-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>全新 EQS 450+ 配备附带 Executive 座椅